.START 

AMES DEPARTMENT STORES Inc., Rocky Hill, Conn., sold $135 million of 7 1/2% convertible subordinated debentures, due 2014.
The debentures of this discount retailer are convertible into common stock of the company at a conversion price of $21.50 a share.
The debentures are not redeemable before Oct. 15, 1992.
Wertheim Schroder & Co. was lead underwriter.
Proceeds, about $131.5 million, will be used to repay bank debt. 

